[SN]TITLE[SN]
London kids on high air pollution: 'Our eyes start stinging'

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
Air pollution in some parts of London has been so bad recently, that the Mayor of London has decided to use the highest pollution level alert for the first time.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
29 January 2017 Last updated at 14:18 GMT
Students at a school in the heart of London tell us what it's like living in a place where the pollution levels are so bad...
